      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "\r\n* 修改当前标题的滚动判定逻辑：标题起始位置一旦越过顶部阅读线，即视为已读，自动高亮下一个标题\r\n* 点击目录可立即定位，高亮随后会继续随滚动更新\r\n* 编辑时目录会跟随光标所在章节\r\n* 阅读模式与编辑模式下的体验更加一致\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n* Modify active heading detection during scrolling: once a heading’s start position passes the top reading line, it is considered completed and the next heading is highlighted\r\n* Clicking a TOC item highlights it instantly, then resumes following scrolling\r\n* In editor mode, the TOC follows the current cursor position\r\n* More consistent behavior across reading and editing modes\r\n",
