      "description": "* 新增 TOC 条目文字大小设置 #1 \r\n* 通过缓存标题数据优化 TOC 更新时机，减少频繁闪动\r\n* 自动移除 TOC 文本中的 Markdown 语法，使目录更干净清晰\r\n* 调整紧凑模式的样式\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n* A new text size setting for TOC entries has been added #1 \r\n* Optimize the TOC update timing by caching title data to reduce frequent flashing\r\n* Automatically remove Markdown syntax from TOC text to make the table of contents cleaner and clearer\r\n* Adjust the style of the compact mode\r\n",
