      "description": "* 解决点击目录跳转不准确的问题，定位更加精准\r\n* 修复阅读模式下重复标题导致的滚动高亮异常\r\n* 统一 source 模式与 preview 模式下的高亮体验\r\n* 增强 TOC 的滚动反馈与整体可视性\r\n* 引入全新的动态紧凑 TOC 模式\r\n\r\n  * 以右对齐的简约条状形式呈现\r\n  * 悬停即可平滑展开\r\n  * 支持动态 Tooltip 信息提示\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n* Fixed inaccurate TOC click navigation for more precise positioning\r\n* Resolved scroll highlighting issues caused by duplicate headings in reading mode\r\n* Aligned highlight behavior between source mode and preview mode\r\n* Enhanced TOC scrolling feedback and overall visibility\r\n* Introduced a new dynamic compact TOC mode\r\n\r\n  * Displayed as a minimal right aligned vertical bar\r\n  * Smoothly expands on hover\r\n  * Dynamically shows tooltips for better context\r\n",
